high_descs: Step to the right to face the card on the living room table.
Pick up the card on the living room table.
Turn left and step forward to face the arm chair.
Place the card in the arm chair.
Step to the left to face the card on the table.
Pick up the card on the table.
Step right to face the arm chair.
Place the card in the arm chair.
anns.task_desc: To move two cards to the arm chair to the left of the living room table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the coffee table.
Pick up the red credit card off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk over to the chair in front of you.
Put the credit card on the middle of the front edge of the seat of the chair.
Turn left and walk towards the door, then turn right and walk up to the round black table in the corner of the room.
Pick up the credit card off of the round black table.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk forward, turn left again to face the chair with the credit card on it.
Put the credit card on the seat of the chair to the right of the card that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Walk over to the right side of the coffee table.
Pick up the credit card from the front edge of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk to the chair straight ahead.
Put the credit card down on the chair.
Walk to the small black table to the left of the chair.
Pick up the credit card next to the lamp.
Walk back to the chair to the right of the black table.
Put the credit card down on the chair to the right of the other one.
anns.task_desc: To move two credit cards to the chair.
